Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.39,main,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the direct approach where we become \Ntitans who overwhelm our enemies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.13,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,I see you understand something, pink fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.41,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Power is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.90,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,With enough power,\N your enemies will never outdo you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.96,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,How do we become titans, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.93,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,I found out the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:59.44,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently in space, if you bite your \Nown thumb, you can turn into a titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.53,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,To think it was so simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.64,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.20,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,I actually grew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.11,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.28,main,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll work for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.97,main,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I grew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.12,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,You all did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.15,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,I had better go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.22,italics,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.82,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,Right, this is how it worked last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.19,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're all set to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.22,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Time to invade some enemy nations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:24.53,italicstop,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for riding with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.72,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.73,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Something's happening to my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.53,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why'd you all shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.40,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Is this treachery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.37,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. I think it must be hereditary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.37,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,You have good genetics, Kaede-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.22,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,How could you all be so mean \Nand leave me like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.54,main,Miria,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.54,italicstop,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.98,main,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Miria-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.05,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Pink fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:44.85,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be stuck like this!\N I want to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.49,main,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, wait a second—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.82,italics,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.61,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... To obliterate \Nus after a mere two blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.80,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief, calm down for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.33,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gone... You want to \Nbe with them, don't you, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.14,main,Haruto,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, please! Stay away, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.03,italics,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.99,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.67,main,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,The road to the Game Club's \Nconquest is still a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.20,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.92,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugen Higo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:30.20,sign_13164_142_Grandma,Lantern sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1238,1)}Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:30.20,sign_13164_143_Ryugen__Higo,Banner sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1238,1)}Ryugen\N Higo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.06,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,It's a term for baseless rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:30.20,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,It naturally refers to rumors that are \Nbeing spread that have no basis in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:35.65,sign_13493_147_Grandma,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:34.89,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,In 1973, there was a toilet paper panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:42.36,sign_13164_142_Grandma,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:42.36,sign_13164_143_Ryugen__Higo,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugen\N Higo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.60,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the oil shock at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:41.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the government announced there \Nwould be paper rationing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:46.51,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, people started to \Nfear they would run out of toilet paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:46.50,sign_13493_147_Grandma,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:50.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a result began \Nbuying it up excessively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:54.10,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,had just turned twenty, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:08.78,sign_13493_147_Grandma,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.52,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,You'd go to the bathroom in a department \Nstore or use a public bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and there'd be no toilet paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.80,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine the kind of shock that'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.67,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,If you went to a public restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.99,top,,0000,0000,0000,,your only choice would be to \Npray-per for paper! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:16.24,sign_14746_158__Pray_per_for_Pa,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"{\c&H31fff7&}Pray-per {\c&Hffffff&}for Paper"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.24,top,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Prayer for a square, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.03,sign_13164_142_Grandma,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.03,sign_13164_143_Ryugen__Higo,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugen\N Higo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:30.90,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,What is with you?! It's not like virtual-san \Nis looking all the time, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:35.76,sign_15328_161_This_segment_is_,Blackboard sign,0000,0000,0000,,This segment is called\N{\c&He9e4e8&\fs16} Let's Go! To Class
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:39.73,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wish spring vacation \Nwould get here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:43.27,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,We just got done with winter vacation!\NIn a rush much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:48.81,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,But you always tend to wonder when the next \Nvacation is after you finish one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.74,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean! \NEven if you got plenty of rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.21,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,You still end up wondering \Nwhen the next one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.28,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy to start slacking \Noff during vacation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.78,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you're always \Nslacking off, Hinata-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.10,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.15,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just practicing for \Nvideo games in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:07.39,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, during vacation I continue \Nmy proper, disciplined lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I never notice much of a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.33,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,The classy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:10.84,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.66,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the sound of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.17,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive! Erotic, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.47,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.30,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's quite normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.97,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,What? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.48,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,What was that shaking?! \NAnd is it suddenly hot—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.61,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.95,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a volcano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.76,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.38,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the heat. Can't stand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.24,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Why's there a volcano outside the classroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.17,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,The heat's gonna kill us! We better evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:41.23,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we evacuate? \NThere's lava everywhere outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.39,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave the building, we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.21,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.82,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Class Prez?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.23,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.10,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing remarkable. \NIt's no different than every day life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.87,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, it's not! \NThere usually aren't volcanoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.34,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,What are a few volcanoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.54,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,If you watch movies, there are \Nbound to be volcanoes showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.38,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,So hot! Dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.38,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally normal, if you \Nthink of it as a sauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.84,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,The volcano's erupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.69,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course a volcano would erupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.55,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're all \Nmaking far too much fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.02,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of this as our usual classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.74,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. The usual classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.79,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.86,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.86,main,Others,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.90,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best today again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.03,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.49,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.78,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even manage that, Akari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.78,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey... is that... magma headed this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.48,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Siro-san, the volcano \Nexploded and the magma shot forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so that's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.40,main,Peanut{same as text},0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring the heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:41.02,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! If we don't do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.99,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna hit us! We'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.79,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.20,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,A volcano explodes, shooting magma about,\N and it's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.86,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'd die! It's totally normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.76,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is it normal to die like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.92,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.73,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.70,main,Peanut,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.64,sign_19792_231_To_Be_Continued,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(301,1)}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.34,main,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:16.04,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,One-two, one-two, one-two, one-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:16.04,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello... Hello... Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.52,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Gori-chan, you've got a \Nspring in your step today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.23,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:20.56,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.33,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.73,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you win a lottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.48,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.51,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Did the total at checkout \Nturn out to be 777 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.23,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.28,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You lost some weight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.71,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,You seem lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.77,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I was peeling a banana, right?\N Since I'm on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.14,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, Gori-chan, you're such a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.83,sign_20981_239_Fuji_Aoi_Park,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji Aoi Park
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.04,main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.26,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.02,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble, big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:49.40,main,Sign/Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble, Akari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.37,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-chan, there's big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.05,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:57.20,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai-san! We've got really big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.23,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,What, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.15,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with the pen name \N"Takeru-kun" is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.11,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Here, read it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:05.39,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,"Akari-san, hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.17,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.44,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,"The other day, I had a \Nmeeting with my friend,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.08,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,"but I overslept and was an hour late,\N and they were furious."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:15.91,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,"They haven't talked to me since.\N What should I do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.95,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Such a hot voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.99,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,But y'know, people get so mad when \Nyou oversleep and miss stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.03,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.13,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he should buy some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.17,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:27.96,sign_22282_260_Akari_MEMO_When_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Akari MEMO\N{\c&H2e2e29&\fs28}When you oversleep, bring snacks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:25.82,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,A peace offering?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.56,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,But what kind of snacks should \Nit be, what would be best?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.63,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe bales of rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.08,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Just one bale, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.00,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.25,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,But in your case, Takeru, maybe take two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:36.77,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.27,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, though.\N Takeru-kun wants to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.61,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he wants to patch things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.15,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'd be best, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.91,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:52.32,sign_23042_274_Hikari,Signs; right/left,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:52.32,sign_23042_275_Yami,Signs; right/left,0000,0000,0000,,Yami
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:53.20,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, there's only one real answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.83,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since it was his fault, he should apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting so \Nworked up for, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.48,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop that! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.55,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.51,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't say things \Nthat'll only make it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just take him to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.46,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up your body so freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. You handle it, then, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.69,main,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:22.18,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?! Mirai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.62,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was thinking too hard there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.33,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.45,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, to pen name Takeru-kun! \NHere's the bottom line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.66,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?! She's going \Nto show her bottom! Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.72,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for last time, \Nyou set up another meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.03,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,and then oversleep by an hour again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.10,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of being on time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:43.47,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,And then, you suddenly grab your friend when \Nthey're about to angrily leave, from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.06,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,And be like, "I'm sorry, the sight of \Nyou standing there was just so lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally fixated and couldn't move."\N Something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.88,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,That seems really romantic, \Nbut isn't it a little bold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:14:08.73,sign_24957_301_Virtual_Kabuki_c,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual Kabuki-cho
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.44,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.15,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,And then, after getting worked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.04,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,the two of them start ****ing and ****ing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.45,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,before vanishing into the lights \Nof late night Kabuki-cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.45,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,How lewd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.23,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it though, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:08.76,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,But it said "friend"! What if it's \None of Takeru-kun's male friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.50,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that'll do for today!\N See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.03,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Come again! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.20,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll actually serve \Nyou something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.65,sign_25786_311_Big_Trouble__Aka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(321,1)}Big Trouble!\NAkari-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:27.95,sign_25916_312_Hinata_chan_Head,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,980)}Hinata-chan Heads to\N{\fs30}School
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.51,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for a pork bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.74,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,almost time for a pork bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.75,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.17,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,It's near the end of the game. \NFour survivors, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:44.93,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,From the sound of gunfire, I'm sure there \Nare two enemies at 1 and 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.70,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,There's a field in the center \Nof the area with good visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.17,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the other one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.57,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,Is he in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:57.28,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,If I waltz out into the field, I'm going \Nto come under fire from three directions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.97,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,and that'll be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.54,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:04.35,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think up a way to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.59,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.19,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.05,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.66,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.79,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no, not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.19,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,You look really intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.74,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,A-A pork bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.32,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go get a pork bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.59,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.93,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are yummy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.27,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.16,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,See you... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.71,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,Pork bowls are best for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.81,sign_27805_338_Hinata_chan_Head,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan Heads to\N{\fs30} School
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.84,main,Kerin,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual-san is looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.09,main,Kerin,0000,0000,0000,,Blow them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:16:30.74,sign_28021_341_Trivia_Diner,Watermark,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3496,1)}Trivia\NDiner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.82,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Tsukino Mito-chan! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.49,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,I am so fed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.96,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get some trivia on chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.36,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.74,main,Sign/VO,0000,0000,0000,,Trivia, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.62,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:57.28,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Columbus was the first \NEuropean to encounter chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.22,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time chocolate \Nwas just a bitter drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.24,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,so he apparently had very \Nlittle interest in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.97,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate's also supposed to have \Nvarious positive health effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:09.08,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,with a woman who was 122 before \Npassing away saying she would
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:12.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,eat 900 grams of chocolate a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.88,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,One other thing, if you eat \Nchocolate and gum together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.36,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,the cocoa butter will melt the gum,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:20.06,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,so it's generally recommended that \Nyou don't have them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.00,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.72,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Your trivia is always so handy, Siro-san.
