Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:44.22,sign_29742_360_Pen_Name__Tsurum,Pink Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Pen Name: {\fs20}Tsurumaki Kazuya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.59,main,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mikurira Lala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.85,main,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite foods are uncooked \Nham and strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.40,main,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,My talents are the vaulting \Nhorse and singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.26,main,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:51.92,sign_30135_365_It_s_3_PM__Class,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(988,477)}It's {\c&H5CDEE9&}3 PM{\c&HF5D08D&},\NClass President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.56,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I wonder who it's going to be today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.73,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kenmochi Rikiya-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.31,main,Sword,0000,0000,0000,,It's Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.75,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, the kanji were so \Nsimilar that I got mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.89,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Class Prez, what is this? \NWhy did you lock me in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.74,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Kenmochi-san! \NLet's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.52,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,We're now going to begin the \Nultimate decision committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.78,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you the best of luck in \Nchoosing the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.08,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,How bossy can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.82,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Here is today's subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.44,main,Sign{also the dialog},0000,0000,0000,,Subject: which kind of on-air trouble \Nwould you choose, as a streamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.99,main,Sign{also the dialog},0000,0000,0000,,A) Your drunken mother interrupts a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.98,main,Sign{also the dialog},0000,0000,0000,,B) The game you were streaming \Nturns out to be BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.62,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,B actually happened to you before, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.23,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I thought it \Nwas a simple typing game,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then all of a sudden a very \Nexplicit BL scene appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.67,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with that in mind, \Nwhich would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:38.64,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Good question. I guess I'd pick A,\N your drunken mother interrupts a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.67,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.91,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,The sort of thing that used to \Nhappen regularly with live streams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.71,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Right, and sometimes it actually \Nmade the stream more entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.88,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thing could often go viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.48,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:52.12,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,And your drunken mother wouldn't be \Nlikely to get you banned by barging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:56.82,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Whereas with the BL game, if it's \Nexplicit enough, you could get banned for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.80,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.83,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,What could a mother do to get \Nyou banned, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:04.26,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she's drunk, she could \Nsuddenly start stripping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.01,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.69,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, that's the bell for 3 PM,\Nso it's time to announce the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer is B), the game you \Nwere streaming turns out to be BL!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.04,main,Toya,0000,0000,0000,,Was there any point in even \Ngetting my opinion then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.74,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That's how I went viral, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.68,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda streamer is worried \Nabout getting banned, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.48,sign_32989_400_It_s_3PM__Class_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(349,1)}It's {\c&H5CDEE9&}3 PM{\c&HF5D08D&},\NClass President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.67,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual-san is looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.12,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you look, Uma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:33.35,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,There's no stopping now! \NVirtual-san is looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.02,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm Otori Kohaku, 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:43.04,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls me Unity-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:47.42,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,As to why... aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.79,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.48,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:55.53,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Not the bamboo spear! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.05,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.09,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:04.05,sign_34202_412_Unity_chan_Wants,TL of sign,0000,0000,0000,,Unity-{\c&H0996e8&}chan Wants {\c&H3e466c&}to\N{\c&H01f0db&}Roll {\c&Hf4bc10&}Around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.59,main,Kohaku,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just stream that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.25,main,Sign/voices,0000,0000,0000,,Kerin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:12.43,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hime, are there really dark \Nelves in a cave like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.10,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,One of the villagers said he \Nsaw one leaving this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.87,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask Villager B, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:21.20,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,B was walking into a wall, \Nso I left him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:25.38,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be dangerous if \Nthey were so close to an town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.37,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so we have to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.31,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hime, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.06,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.68,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Keblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.14,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! It noticed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.62,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:20:03.44,sign_35235_426_For_various_reas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(318,1)}For various reasons, we will be\N presenting this segment in still images.\N Next week, look forward\N to the full animated version.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.05,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.52,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ninnomono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.69,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.96,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you manage that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.30,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda felt like it'd work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.73,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.73,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.72,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Nin! Nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.08,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.82,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,The Keblins are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:56.79,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Quit trying to take Hime's pants off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.70,main,Kerin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.76,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.41,main,Kerin,0000,0000,0000,,Time to blow it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.11,sign_36069_441_See_you_next_wee,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,See you next week!
