Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.94,main,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, your wife, Master, Ekaki Makuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:20.55,main,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,I want to use my Kamieshi \NPower to care for you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.25,main,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.70,main,Cat,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
