Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.75,main,Uma,0000,0000,0000,,Please, listen, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.22,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, dear horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.55,main,Uma,0000,0000,0000,,There's this girl who I \Nwant to tell how I feel—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.12,top,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:41.99,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.48,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,I did my laundry when there \Nwas some tissue in my pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.37,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,and my clothes ended up covered in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:51.96,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:57.08,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,At times like that, using the \Ndryer or some dry fabric softener
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,should make it easier to get the tissue off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.08,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:03.01,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the option \Nof using a lint roller,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.92,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,and on the odd side of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you can use the nets that produce \Nare sold in to pick it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.29,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You can try any of those ways out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.58,main,Sora,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.02,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,May you be virtually blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.88,main,Uma,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.54,main,Gori,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor. This is \N"Virtual-san is looking."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.69,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we've got a letter to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.77,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,This is from pen name "Sleight of Hand, \NSlight of Mouth." Thanks for writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.78,main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.44,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,"Good evening, everyone. You're all incredibly\N beautiful, and very popular online."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.08,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,"But who among you is the most \Npopular? Please tell me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.58,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear I'm popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.75,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Well everyone, who do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.33,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Popular... Who's most popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.89,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whoever has the biggest fluffy \Nmelon breads is usually the most popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.92,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then who does that make number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.19,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'd have to compare to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:54.22,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everyone, step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:55.09,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody line up.{timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.29,top,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.10,main,Akari,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, show them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.93,main,Hime,0000,0000,0000,,I'm young! I'm too young, \Ndon't make me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.60,main,Hinata,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.73,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,So, that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:10.22,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,The most popular member among the \Nsix of us is Cyber Girl Siro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.18,main,Shiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you were just guessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:13.91,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:15.55,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,And now the segment's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.05,main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, guessing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:20.85,main,Mito,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's it for this week!\NSee you next time on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:24.17,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual-san is looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.53,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:14.09,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Virtual Youtuber who's getting \Na second crack at life as a young girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:15.54,sign_41729_493_Mochi_Hiyoko,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(321,1)}Mochi Hiyoko
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:15.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochi Hiyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:19.18,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've all thought about \Nwanting to be a little girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:21.96,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a medicine that can make \Nthat dream come true... right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.63,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magical medicine that can turn \Nyou into a little girl right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:28.46,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet everyone would be happy \Nif we were all little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:30.80,main,Hiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, be a little girl!
